text: Manushi Chhillar (born 14 May 1997) in Haryana, India is Indian model, winner of Miss India 2017 and the winner of the Miss World 2017 beauty contest. She is listed in 6th indian women to won Miss World beauty pageant after Priyanka Chopra. She also won the title of Miss Photogenic in Miss India competition. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Indian beauty pageant winners Category:Miss World winners Category:Living people Category:Indian models
